808
01:13:38,790 --> 01:13:40,832
Danny Archer. This is Maddy Bowen.

809
01:13:41,000 --> 01:13:44,086
- Hello. How are you?
- Very well, thank you.

810
01:13:44,253 --> 01:13:46,004
Welcome brother.

811
01:13:46,172 --> 01:13:48,924
I am Solomon Vandy, from Shenge.

812
01:13:49,634 --> 01:13:51,718
What should I make of your companions?

813
01:13:53,387 --> 01:13:55,722
He- She is... They are journalists.

814
01:13:56,057 --> 01:13:57,265
Ah. And I suppose you are, too.

815
01:13:58,893 --> 01:14:01,186
I'm the cameraman?

816
01:14:03,815 --> 01:14:06,733
The Belgians were the first
to chop off limbs in Africa.

817
01:14:06,901 --> 01:14:11,279
King Leopold took one hand
for every hundredth slave in the Congo...

818
01:14:11,447 --> 01:14:13,532
...to keep them in line.

819
01:14:14,200 --> 01:14:17,119
Many of these children
were taken by the RUF.

820
01:14:17,286 --> 01:14:19,287
We have taken them back.

821
01:14:19,455 --> 01:14:22,541
Some of them have been
made to do horrible things.

822
01:14:22,708 --> 01:14:25,752
We are trying
to bring them back to life.

823
01:14:25,920 --> 01:14:27,546
Let me show you.

