825
01:14:33,219 --> 01:14:35,095
What's your excuse?

826
01:14:35,888 --> 01:14:41,226
Well, it's gotten hard to go back
to sipping lattes and talking interest rates.

827
01:14:41,477 --> 01:14:44,104
So you're an action junkie, huh?

828
01:14:45,064 --> 01:14:47,357
Three out of five ex-boyfriends
recently polled...

829
