who gets what, you know?

879
01:18:41,634 --> 01:18:44,677
Ivory, oil, gold:

880
01:18:45,638 --> 01:18:47,389
Diamonds.

881
01:18:50,643 --> 01:18:53,603
So one day I decided,
"Fuck it," you know?

882
01:18:54,230 --> 01:18:55,814
"I'm gonna get mine. "

883
01:18:55,981 --> 01:18:57,565
You gonna steal his diamond?

884
01:19:05,074 --> 01:19:08,785
