01:21:33,931 --> 01:21:35,974
Oh, shit. Keep moving, huh?

906
01:21:36,141 --> 01:21:37,892
- What?
- Drive at them. They'll panic.

907
01:21:38,060 --> 01:21:40,311
Do you know where the word
"infantry" comes from?

908
01:21:40,479 --> 01:21:43,815
It means "child soldier. "
